description: Welcome to 597 E 2nd Street, the perfect condo alternative on South Boston’s coveted East Side. This 3-bedroom, 2.5-bath single-family residence spans three levels, blending designer finishes with modern functionality. The open-concept main floor features a chef-inspired kitchen with Bosch appliances, a farmhouse sink, and striking Cygnet Drift quartz countertops, flowing seamlessly into spacious dining and living areas. The top floor is a private retreat with a full primary suite, complete with an en-suite bath and large closet. Two additional bedrooms and a full bath on the second level are perfect for family, guests, or a home office. A private patio creates an ideal setting for entertaining or relaxing outdoors, while the rare convenience of off-street parking enhances daily living. With every detail thoughtfully designed and an unbeatable location close to South Boston’s vibrant shops, restaurants, beaches, and the Seaport, this home truly offers the best of city living!
